---
---
<section class="faq-section">
  <div class="faq-container">
    <div class="faq-header">
      <p class="faq-subtitle">QUESTIONS, ANSWERED</p>
      <h2 class="faq-title">Frequently asked questions</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-list">
      <details class="faq-item" open>
        <summary class="faq-summary">
          <span class="faq-question">How do the motorized louvers operate, and do they close automatically?</span>
          <span class="faq-icon"></span>
        </summary>
        <div class="faq-content">
          <p>Our motorized louvers are operated via a sleek, weather-resistant remote control or a smartphone app. For ultimate peace of mind, we can integrate smart rain sensors that automatically close the louvers completely at the very first drop of rain, protecting your outdoor furniture.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-summary">
          <span class="faq-question">How does the "Call to Verify Supply Availability" work?</span>
          <span class="faq-icon"></span>
        </summary>
        <div class="faq-content">
          <p></p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-summary">
          <span class="faq-question">Can the pergolas withstand high winds and the hot SoCal sun?</span>
          <span class="faq-icon"></span>
        </summary>
        <div class="faq-content">
          <p></p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-summary">
          <span class="faq-question">Can you automate my gate?</span>
          <span class="faq-icon"></span>
        </summary>
        <div class="faq-content">
          <p>Yes. We specialize in smart automation. We can integrate whisper-quiet motors, remote keypads, and smartphone apps (like Ring or Nest) directly into your custom gate design.</p>
        </div>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
 .faq-section {
 width: 100%;
 background-color: #ffffff;
 padding: 93px 0 100px 0;
 display: flex;
 justify-content: center;
 }

 .faq-container {
 width: 695px;
 max-width: 100%;
 display: flex;
 flex-direction: column;
 }

 .faq-header {
 text-align: center;
 margin-bottom: 50px;
 }
 
 .faq-subtitle {
 font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
 font-weight: 600; /* Bold */
 font-size: 12px;
 line-height: 16px;
 letter-spacing: 2.64px;
 color: #2C65B0;
 text-transform: uppercase;
 margin: 0 0 15px 0;
 }

 .faq-title {
 font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
 font-weight: 800; /* Bold */
 font-size: 45px;
 line-height: 45px;
 letter-spacing: -0.94px;
 color: #14110E;
 margin: 0;
 }

 .faq-list {
 display: flex;
 flex-direction: column;
 }

 .faq-item {
 border-bottom: 1px solid #2C65B0;
 overflow: hidden;
 }

 /* No border bottom on the last item to match typical design unless requested, wait screenshot has border? I will leave border-bottom on all except last */
 .faq-item:last-child {
 border-bottom: none;
 }

 .faq-summary {
 display: flex;
 justify-content: space-between;
 align-items: center;
 padding: 30px 0;
 cursor: pointer;
 list-style: none; /* Remove default triangle */
 }

 .faq-summary::-webkit-details-marker {
 display: none; /* Safari */
 }

 .faq-question {
 font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
 font-weight: 800; /* Bold */
 font-size: 18px;
 line-height: 28px;
 color: #14110E;
 max-width: 94%;
 white-space: nowrap;
 overflow: hidden;
 text-overflow: ellipsis;
 }

 .faq-icon {
 width: 24px;
 height: 24px;
 background-image: url('/assets/images/faq/+.svg');
 background-size: contain;
 background-repeat: no-repeat;
 background-position: center;
 flex-shrink: 0;
 transition: transform 0.3s ease;
 }

 /* When details is open, change icon */
 .faq-item[open] .faq-icon {
 background-image: url('/assets/images/faq/-.svg');
 }

 .faq-content {
 padding-bottom: 30px;
 animation: slideDown 0.3s ease-out;
 }

 .faq-content p {
 font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
 font-weight: 400; /* Regular */
 font-size: 16px;
 line-height: 26px;
 color: #635C57;
 margin: 0;
 }

 @keyframes slideDown {
 from {
 opacity: 0;
 transform: translateY(-10px);
 }
 to {
 opacity: 1;
 transform: translateY(0);
 }
 }

 /* ─── RESPONSIVE ───────────────────────────────────────── */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
  .faq-section {
  padding: 34px 20px 60px 20px !important;
  }

  .faq-header {
  margin-bottom: 35px !important;
  }

  .faq-title {
  font-size: 24px !important;
  line-height: 27px !important;
  letter-spacing: -0.9px !important;
  }

  .faq-summary {
  min-height: 72px !important;
  padding: 10px 0 !important;
  }
  
  .faq-question {
  font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif !important;
  font-weight: 800 !important;
  font-size: 18px !important;
  line-height: 26px !important;
  color: #14110E !important;
  }

  .faq-content p {
  font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif !important;
  font-weight: 400 !important;
  font-size: 16px !important;
  line-height: 26px !important;
  color: #635C57 !important;
  }
  }
</style>
